  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package deliberately omits acceptanceCriteria from several CredibilityFactor entries (W-AR-01 weakener) while declaring requiredLevel, leaving the rationale for those levels undocumented in structured form.",
